messages.message:
Brian
I have been working in the health industry and the air force sticks out in my mind as being really important.  What are you up to?
I'm a little partial to how important the AF is.  I'm currently a Public Health Technician out east...

Brian
I love what they are doing really.  Lots of smart people.  I need a job with smart people.
There are a few not so smart people that slip through, lol... but it's pretty much a corporation where people are held accountable.  Are u looking to join?

Brian
Absolutely. I love accountability.
I use Google calendar as my to-do list.
